          "reviewBody": "My son studying in Narayana E techno school M R Nagar branch in 7th std.Teachers are passionate about seeing their students succeed. Especially Deepika madam(class teacher)They are so great about sharing moments of pride they see within our child – their good behaviours and achievements; and they know the importance of getting the parents involved should an issue arise, and do it in a very respectful, approachable manner.\n\nGreat team – great school!",
