            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "A great school especially the pre primary segment. The teachers are taking a very good care of the children. They are doing many activities related to the academics and even for the life skills also. They are celebrating each and every festival and national festival. The children are getting very excited to learn new things. They are having one caretaker for each class (LKG and UKG). They are conducting parent teacher meeting every month and updating the student's performance to the parents. I have very much satisfied with the school and the teachers and with my kid's performance.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
